Title: Those Who Hesitate
Description:
Hm.

There is one who has been counted amongst our number, but is not here.

The draenei.

<Madam Shadow inhales.>

I can taste the Light about him. Go, see to it that he rejoins us.

There is much work to be done.
ObjectivesText: Talk to Initiate Oman in the Darkmoon Faire.
